      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW ORENTHAL (8) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing second (25.37) at Ballarat over 450m. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Good form should continue. HARTLAND WILLOW (4) ran a solid 25.32 when winning over 450m at this track last start. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. SCOTT VICIOUS (6) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (25.80) at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from five attempts. Ready to find winning form. SODA SWAN (7) is a last-start placegetter and was not beaten too far - in the mix again.",
